Package com.github.joncros.remoteSensors

Provides a webapp to check a computer's sensor readings using the jSensors library. Must be run with administrator rights on the computer to be monitored.
See Also:
profesorfalken/jSensors on github, especially jSensors/model
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    Main class, launches the Spring RESTful web service which is consumed by webapp\index.html
    ComponentAdapter
    Uses google's Gson to serialize all of the jsensors (@code Component} objects for this machine into JSON.
    ComponentsController
    Maps the JSON serializing all of the sensor readings for the current machine to http://localhost:8080/sensors.
    test
    Tests the JSensors library by printing sensor readings to the console
